thread.title: Stephanie & Brendan
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Stephanie & Brendan

author: Stephanie & Brendan
title: Stephanie & Brendan
text: Anthony and his team at Nelson Alexander Brunswick were close to flawless in the letting and management of our property. It is clear that we have benefitted immensely from Anthony's years of experience in the rental market of Melbourne's inner north, something other agents simply aren't able to match. He was quick to respond to our queries, found an ideal tenant, and managed the whole process with incredible efficiency and professionalism. An unreserved recommendation.
